{"data":{"remark":{"html":"<!-- **************************************** -->\n<header class='hero simple'>\n<div class='container'>\n<div class='row'>\n<div class='col-xs-12'>\n<div class='hero-block'>\n<h1 id=\"graphile-announcements\"><a href=\"#graphile-announcements\" aria-label=\"graphile announcements permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Graphile Announcements</h1>\n<h3>\n  The latest news on PostGraphile and the Graphile suite\n</h3>\n<br />\n<div class='flex'>\n<a class='button--solid-light' href='/news/postgraphile-version-4-4/'>Latest Announcement <span class='fas fa-fw fa-arrow-right' /></a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</header>\n<!-- **************************************** -->\n<section>\n<div class='container'>\n<div class='row flex-wrap-reverse'>\n<div class='text-center col-xs-12 col-md-9 col-lg-7'>\n<div class='hero-block'>\n<h2 id=\"postgraphile-version-44-released\"><a href=\"#postgraphile-version-44-released\" aria-label=\"postgraphile version 44 released permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>PostGraphile Version 4.4 released</h2>\n<p>Version 4.4 is here, and among other things it adds real-time features including GraphQL subscriptions and live queries!</p>\n<p><a href=\"/news/postgraphile-version-4-4/\">Read more about the latest PostGraphile version here</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class='text-center col-xs-12 col-md-3 col-lg-5 postgraphile-logo-bg'>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<!-- **************************************** -->\n<section>\n<div class='container'>\n<h2 id=\"see-what-people-are-saying\"><a href=\"#see-what-people-are-saying\" aria-label=\"see what people are saying permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>See what people are saying</h2>\n  <div class=\"mw9 ph3-ns flex flex-row flex-wrap\">\n  <div class=\"cf ph2-ns flex flex-wrap\">\n    <article class=\"w-100 w-50-m w-25-ns pa2 center bg-white br3 pa4-ns mv3 ba b--black-10\">\n      <div class=\"tc\">\n        <h1 class=\"f3 di\">Chad F</h1>\n        <h2 class=\"i f5 di\">senior technical lead <a href=\"https://chads.website/development/2018/08/03/How-GraphQL-Saved-My-Project.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"fas fa-external-link-alt\"></span></a></h2>\n        <hr class=\"mw3 bb bw1 b--black-10 db\">\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"lh-copy measure center f6 black-70\">\n        <i class=\"fas fa-quote-left h3 w3 di\" style=\"color: #004081;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n        Thanks for making GraphQL something I can use on my project in a robust way with <strong>minimal effort</strong>. 500-1500 requests per second on a single server is pretty awesome.&nbsp;<i class=\"fas fa-quote-right h3 w3 di\" style=\"color: #004081;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n      </p>\n    </article>\n    <article class=\"w-100 w-50-m w-25-ns pa2 center bg-white br3 pa4-ns mv3 ba b--black-10\" style=\"flex-grow: 1\">\n      <div class=\"tc\">\n        <h1 class=\"f3 di\">Bradley A</h1>\n        <h2 class=\"i f5 di\">CTO <a href=\"https://twitter.com/bradleyayers/status/1012557510346080256\" target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"fab fa-twitter\"></i></a></h2>\n        <hr class=\"mw3 bb bw1 b--black-10 db\">\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"lh-copy measure center f6 black-70\">\n         <i class=\"fas fa-quote-left h3 w3 di\" style=\"color: #004081;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n         I setup my backend to use PostGraphile directly when querying the local database. It's removed a bunch of hand-written SQL, added type-safety to verify Postgres schema compatibility, and <strong>created a more consistent dev experience for frontend/backend code.</strong>&nbsp;<i class=\"fas fa-quote-right h3 w3 di\" style=\"color: #004081;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n      </p>\n    </article>\n    <article class=\"w-100 w-50-m w-25-ns pa2 center bg-white br3 pa4-ns mv3 ba b--black-10\" style=\"flex-grow: 1\">\n      <div class=\"tc\">\n        <h1 class=\"f3 di\">Sam L</h1> \n        <h2 class=\"i f5 di\">full stack developer <a href=\"https://gitter.im/graphile/postgraphile?at=5b65d555e9ab53770c8c41a1\"target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"fas fa-external-link-alt\"></i></a></h2>\n        <hr class=\"mw3 bb bw1 b--black-10 db\">\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"lh-copy measure center f6 black-70\">\n        <i class=\"fas fa-quote-left h3 w3 di\" style=\"color: #004081;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n        This project, Benjie's handling of it, the docs, support, and community is awesome all around. <strong>PostGraphile is a powerful, idomatic, and elegant tool.</strong>&nbsp;<i class=\"fas fa-quote-right h3 w3 di\" style=\"color: #004081;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n      </p>\n    </article>\n    <article class=\"w-100 w-50-m w-25-ns pa2 center bg-white br3 pa4-ns mv3 ba b--black-10\" style=\"flex-grow: 1\">\n      <div class=\"tc\">\n        <h1 class=\"f3 di\">Max D</h1>\n        <h2 class=\"i f5 di\">software consultant <a href=\"https://twitter.com/maxdesiatov/status/1001419221102940160\" target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"fab fa-twitter\"></i></a></h2>\n        <hr class=\"mw3 bb bw1 b--black-10 db\">\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"lh-copy measure center f6 black-70\">\n        <i class=\"fas fa-quote-left h3 w3 di\" style=\"color: #004081;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n         Recently I launched a few mobile and web apps using GraphQL, Great stuff, not least thanks to wonderful PostGraphile and Apollo. <strong>At this point, itâ€™s quite hard for me to come back and enjoy working with REST.</strong>&nbsp;<i class=\"fas fa-quote-right h3 w3 di\" style=\"color: #004081;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n      </p>\n    </article>\n  </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<!-- **************************************** -->\n<section>\n<div class='container'>\n<div class='row flex-wrap-reverse'>\n<div class='text-center col-xs-12 col-md-9 col-lg-7'>\n<div class='hero-block'>\n<h2 id=\"postgraphile-version-41---better-webpackability\"><a href=\"#postgraphile-version-41---better-webpackability\" aria-label=\"postgraphile version 41   better webpackability permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>PostGraphile Version 4.1 - better webpackability!</h2>\n<p>Building upon the huge performance gains found in Version 4, the release of Version 4.1 has a huge improvement to startup performance in serverless environments. This update also brings a large number of enhancements including much broader PostgreSQL function support, an enhanced GraphiQL interface, and a lot more helpers for writing plugins.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/news/postgraphile-version-4-1/\">Read more about PostGraphile Version 4.1 here</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<!-- **************************************** -->\n<section>\n<div class='container'>\n<div class='row flex-wrap-reverse'>\n<div class='text-center col-xs-12 col-md-9 col-lg-7'>\n<div class='hero-block'>\n<h2 id=\"postgraphile-version-4-is-here\"><a href=\"#postgraphile-version-4-is-here\" aria-label=\"postgraphile version 4 is here permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>PostGraphile Version 4 is here</h2>\n<p>Version 4 has launched! More performant, more extensible and more customisable than ever before. Easily extend PostGraphile's functionality with plugins developed and shared by the community.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/news/postgraphile-version-4/\">Read more about PostGraphile Version 4 here</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class='text-center col-xs-12 col-md-3 col-lg-5 postgraphile-graphs-average-latency-label'>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<!-- **************************************** -->","frontmatter":{"path":"/news/","title":"News"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/news/","layout":"marketing"}}